{"tid":1148472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【非洲豬瘟】內地運港豬內臟驗出病毒 上水屠房6000隻將全部銷毀","createTime":"2019-05-10T13:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T16:11:49.000Z","uid":54733,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25fd569276d0b87bac9d4328a9455d3ccf747006","tid":1148472,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:10:24.000Z","msg":"食衛局局長陳肇始今晚10時將就一宗非洲豬瘟化驗報告會見記者。據悉，上水一個屠場一個豬內臟證實有病毒，現時屠房內有6000隻豬隻，政府將會全部銷毀，屠房暫停運作消毒。而豬隻是由內地運到本港，相信帶病豬隻已流出市面並有人食用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1498200/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1498200%2F&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=ca3569d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1498200%2F&h=d5f5bb57\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1498200/</a>"},{"pid":"a1f4612f6cb8b369d9ea0698cac9b60ab94ecfbe","tid":1148472,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"163aa49fade44ba50333415fbf1a3aaac7f39111","tid":1148472,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:11:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f35792335bcf5db32ac446b84995422dfd8c8fe0","tid":1148472,"uid":41389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:11:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝支那送大禮</span></span>"},{"pid":"af0e115ca6904041475e3882422c2c07a3764325","tid":1148472,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:11:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>各位香港豬農不要怕<br />\n你還有黨啊！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525bded705d0c9e646206f824d62108848a17a8f","tid":1148472,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci